description: Deletes an existing matchmaking rule set. To delete the rule set, provide the rule set name. Rule sets cannot be deleted if they are currently being used by a matchmaking configuration.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: A unique identifier for the matchmaking rule set to be deleted. (Note: The rule set name is different from the optional 'name' field in the rule set body.) You can use either the rule set name or ARN value.
